Package: zram-writeback
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, ${perl:Depends}, perl, systemd | systemd-tmpfiles, kmod, util-linux
Description: pressure-aware zram recompression and writeback controller
 Perl implementation for configuring and operating zram swap with lz4 primary
 compression, lzo-rle and zstd recompression tiers, idle tracking, writeback
 budgets and PSI-aware policy decisions.
